"""
    Check if a given axis is still or not.
    """
with expected_protocol(ik.newport.AGUC2, ['MR', '1 TS', '2 TS', '2 TS',
    '2 TS'], [], sep='\r\n') as agl:
    with pytest.raises(IOError):
        agl.axis['X'].am_i_still(max_retries=1)
    with pytest.raises(IOError):
        agl.axis['Y'].am_i_still(max_retries=3)
